This is the documentation of how to use Luasofia, 
it is updated every time a release is made.

To see how to develop new features to Luasofia take a look
at the utils module, and to the devel documentation. 

for up-to-date documentation see: http://wiki.github.com/ppizarro/luasofia

The documentation is made using textile, see http://textile.thresholdstate.com/
